<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mihiem Chapa A hungkit tieng zie zing khawvak hawih achun,
 A lopina vak chuh I muh tieng uleh;
 Gamtin leh chitin apat A mite a sap khawm tieng leh,
 Tatsa kikhawp lopi ahi na ding e!

[V2]
 Kikhawpna lien! Kikhawpna lien!
 Hehpihna gam nuoma tatsate kikhawpna lien hina;
 Kikhawpna lien! Kikhawpna lien!
 Chunglam In nuoma tatsate kikhawpna!

[V3]
 2. Nuomsa Isu a thite A sapa a thawh tieng u leh,
 Than khuk thim sung leh tuisuohgiet apat in;
 Taksa se theitalo pun vanah Amah chu tuok unau,
 Kikhawppi lien, lawp um ahi na ding e!

[V4]
 3. I mit un khawpi a umna tamtak vak tak a muh tieng,
 A lui thip leh dam hieu a luong I muh tieng;
 Thihna'n ei khen I guolteu tawh kipak a I kikhawp tieng,
 Khawppi lien kilamtuoh na lopi hina.

[V5]
 4. Lalpen hung kit tei ding ahi, A hungna ding a nai tai,
 Nitiem kipahum chuh I muh tieng u leh;
 Tieng chuleh mitphet kal lo a I vo uhi kitheng ding,
 Amah kawma cheng zing ding I hitau hi.</lyrics>
<title>WHAT A GATHERING</title>
</song>